defs: 1.(slang) awesome, amazing; very cool, very nice Good;
1.calque (a word formed by word-for-word translation of a word in another language); 2.sticker (an adhesive label or decal);

1.first-person singular (eu) present subjunctive of decalcar; 2.third-person singular (ele and ela, also used with você and others) present subjunctive of decalcar; 3.third-person singular (você) affirmative imperative of decalcar; 4.third-person singular (você) negative imperative of decalcar;
